""" Tests of CallableValue """
proxy = utils.CallableValue('flonk')
falsy = utils.CallableValue(False)
app = flask.Flask(__name__)
with app.test_request_context('/bar'):
    assert proxy == 'flonk'
    assert len(proxy) == 5
    assert proxy + 'foo' == 'flonkfoo'
    assert proxy
    assert not falsy
